metadata.description:
Changes

In this experimental music collection I want to involve YOU as a  collector. 

By collecting an edition of Changes you will receive a 5% split (Per edition) on each of the three last songs apart of the Changes EP. These three songs will be ran as Open Editions in the next few weeks upon sellout. 

Additionally, the golden egg winner of Changes will be receiving 50% of the total revenue raised (excluding the Sound.xyz split) on this collection upon sellout. 

I welcome you to join me as a collaborator on the official release of Changes.
